{"id": "1282796830286942268", "channel_id": "1282785275960885328", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "用哈姆林砍過各個模式後，我覺得追憶這張卡3費真正的用意應該是在不虧資源的情況下產生鑰能，塞牙縫的力量是送的", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T20:16:37.553000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282785275960885328", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "推广一下入药溯回 哈姆林", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526"]}
